{
  "stem": "22892.7",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[SIGHS] I used to think, if somebody told me my story, I would never believe him, because I thought it was almost impossible to go through what I did.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And when I tell it, it doesn't seem like it was really that hard.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I mean, when I talk about it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But to live through, minute by minute, and day by day, and hour-- you know, it just seemed endless.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And-- I mean to-- to be afraid of everything-- I mean, it's like you have no friends.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You're totally alone, totally alone.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I mean, the only people who were good, you come in for awhile, and they give you some food, and they like for you to leave, not to stay there.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I mean, just think, for three years, I've never taken a bath.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I never changed clothes-- I mean, unless they disappeared.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They just wore out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it was tough.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But then you hear about these concentration camp people, and they had it like-- they lived through something that is unbearable.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's also, you know-- I'm not trying to compare which is worse, or which is better, but it was tough.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So now, when I tell this story, it's-- it's quite different from the way I used to think.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Well, let's stop here.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
